{"tid":1946316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼約翰遜後　英國衛生大臣夏國賢同樣確診新型肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-27T14:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T14:08:07.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"20ebe6615dbac3535e2b1890c173025ca10ed21c","tid":1946316,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1517313_1_20200327211308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1517313_1_20200327211308.jpg&h=02ed0659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜及衛生大臣夏國賢，先後對新冠病毒測試呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜在社交網站發布影片，指自己出現輕微病徵，包括發燒及持續咳嗽，經檢測證實染病，正自我隔離，會在家中透過視像會議，繼續領導政府對抗疫情的工作，又再次呼籲民眾遵守政府指示，留在家中，強調最終一定會戰勝疫情。<br />\n<br />\n衛生大臣夏國賢其後亦公布自己確診的消息，指自己出現輕微病徵，在醫生建議下接受檢測，證實呈陽性，他會在家中自我隔離，期間繼續工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517313-20200327.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517313-20200327.htm&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fjXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=b3621298\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517313-20200327.htm&h=b2c972ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517313-20200327.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e66e69a48782f94e3ed6ffff314383cbaacff520","tid":1946316,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"Team kill<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8c74711f4385c1f918be6251f95954cda2261c","tid":1946316,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊境唔驗大陸人，<br />\n<br />\n係因為驚踢爆大陸零確診講大話</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bb6569734b8a8010363b63081ea167ccc38878a1","tid":1946316,"uid":343161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-